title: KISS Attack of the Phantom
description: KISS ATTACK OF THE PHANTOM RIPPED FROM KISSOLOGY2. THIS IS THE EUROPEAN THEATRICAL RELEASE FROM 1979. THE U.S.A. RELEASE WAS MADE FOR TV THAT AIRED ON NBC AND TITLED &#039;KISS MEETS THE PHANTOM OF THE PARK&#039;. THE EUROPEAN RELEASE HAS A DIFFERNT SOUNDTRACK W/MUSIC FROM THE SOLO ALBUMS ETC. THE U.S.A. RELEASE HAD MUSIC FROM 1975-77. ALSO INTERESTING OF NOTE IS THE U.S.A. VERSION WAS LAST AVAILABLE IN THE MID 80&#039;S ON GOODTIMES VIDEO VHS. YOU CAN ONLY FIND IT AS A VHS RIP IN POOR QUALITY BOOTLEG. MANY THANKS GO TO KISS FOR FINALLY RERELEASING THIS MOVIE. ENJOY IT!!!
